📚 Key Takeaways

✔ Files provide permanent data storage
✔ `open()` is used to access files
✔ `read()`, `readline()`, and `readlines()` read data
✔ `write()` and `append()` modify files
✔ `with open()` is the safest approach
✔ Different file modes support different operations


